      "type": "ambiguity",
      "description": "The billing model for multi-recipient shipments is unspecified. Is a 3-recipient shipment billed as 1 shipment, 3 shipments, or a base fee plus per-recipient surcharge? This must be defined before implementation as it affects pricing, invoicing, and financial reporting.",
      "affected_stakeholders": ["Finance", "End Users", "Partners"],
      "options": [
        "Bill as a single shipment regardless of recipient count",
