        "Base shipment fee plus incremental per-recipient charge"
      ],
      "recommendation": "Option 3 — base fee plus per-recipient surcharge. This aligns with the physical cost model (one pickup, multiple deliveries) and is fairest to customers while protecting margins."
    },
